{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_07_01_short",
  "title": "川咲さくら 1話 瀕死の遊園地を救います！ (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "さとみさんから聞いたんですけど、サニーピースに\n遊園地からオファーが来たって本当ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from Hashimoto-san that Sunny Peace\ngot an offer from an amusement park‚ is that true?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.4333334048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "遊園地でライブするなんて楽しみです\n遊びに来たお客さんを笑顔にしちゃいますよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so excited to perform live at an amusement park!\nI'll make all the guests smile!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.0666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すまない。乗り気になっているところ悪いが\nその仕事は断るつもりなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry. It's too bad you were looking forward to it‚ but\nI'm going to decline that job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4535204284,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、どうしてですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.353107357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "向こうが指定した日程に、サニピの五人を揃えるのは\nスケジュール的に無理なんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's impossible to get all five members of Sunny Peace together\non the date they specified.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.6345585505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "五人とも個人での仕事が増えてきて\n都合がつかなかったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone's been getting more individual jobs lately\nso we couldn't make it work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4012252171,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんですか……\nみんなで歌いたかったな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is that so…?\nI wanted to sing with everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "先方も残念に思うはずだ。サニピのライブを\n遊園地を立て直すきっかけにしたいと言っていたからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sure they'll be disappointed too. They said they wanted to use\nSunny Peace's concert as a springboard to revive the amusement park.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6640825907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "立て直す……？\nもしかして、その遊園地は経営が苦しいんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Revive…?\nDoes that mean that amusement park is struggling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.8000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "詳しくは分からないが\nお客さんの数が年々減っているのは事実らしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't know the details but it seems that\nthe number of guests has been decreasing year by year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5913860956,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}